      About

      Description

      Lionel Andrés Messi, also known as Leo Messi, is an Argentine professional footballer who plays as a forward for Ligue 1 club Paris Saint-Germain and captains the Argentina national team. Wikipedia
      Born: 24 June 1987 (age 35 years), Rosario, Argentina
      Height: 1.69 m
      Current teams: Paris Saint-Germain F.C. (#30 / Forward), Argentina national football team (#10 / Forward)
      Spouse: Antonela Roccuzzo (m. 2017)
      Shoe size: 10
      Children: Mateo Messi Roccuzzo, Thiago Messi Roccuzzo, Ciro Messi Roccuzzo
      Salary: 4.1 crores USD (2022)
